Author: DuckieIsMyHero88
Text: I understand this feeling so much. It's basically how I feel right now. *small rant sorry* I'm working a shit job at Walmart where I lift heavy shit all day so I'm constantly sore. My paycheck is shit, so while I have enough to pay my car note (because I just haaaad to have the suv) I don't have much spending money. At this rate I'll never save up enough to go back to school. And I'm constantly in the state of either sleeping, about to start sobbing, or wanting to start self harming again.   TL:DR I'm here if you need someone to listen to you ‚ù§‚ù§
